urged the international community to exert pressure on Israel to
withdraw from other occupied lands and release all Lebanese
prisoners.
</P>
<P>
Kharrazi and Annan also discussed the process of implementing U.
N. resolutions on Palestine, critical situation in Afghanistan and
issues related to the fighting of narcotic drugs.
</P>
<P>
The U.N. secretary-general arrived here Sunday on the first leg
of his week-long Middle East tour. He is also expected to visit
Egypt, Lebanon, the Palestinian self-rule area and Syria. 
