proposed the launching of "the Forum of Chinese Online Media."
More than 20 news media including Xinhua News Agency, Guangming
Daily, Economic Daily, China Central Broadcasting Station, China
Central Television Station and China Radio International have
expressed their willingness to join the forum.
</P>
<P>
According to the proposal, the forum will organize annual
seminar, conduct academic exchanges, training of professionals and
academic research among traditional and on-line news media to
promote the construction and development of on-line news media.
